Udhihirisho wa pepo wabaya

0:00:13.720,0:00:17.520
Kufunguliwa  katika Jina la Yesu

0:00:17.520,0:00:19.880
Sitazungumza.

0:00:19.880,0:00:21.520
Yeye ni mke wangu.

0:00:21.520,0:00:23.940
Umemfanyia nini huyu?

0:00:23.940,0:00:29.860
Hawezi kuolewa kwa sababu  ni wangu.

0:00:29.860,0:00:31.220
Umefanya nini kwa familia yake?

0:00:31.220,0:00:38.660
kukwama, hakuna maendeleo - hataweza kamwe kutumia cheti chake.

0:00:38.660,0:00:40.080
Umefanya nini katika kazi yake?

0:00:40.080,0:00:43.820
Atakuwa anafanya kazi na kuacha.

